<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to COP Abu Dhabi!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>We are delighted to welcome you as a new member of the Church of Pentecost Abu Dhabi! Your membership application has been approved, and we look forward to growing together in faith and fellowship.</p>
    
    <p>Here are some important next steps:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Complete your member profile</li>
      <li>Join a ministry</li>
      <li>Connect with your assigned deacon/deaconess</li>
      <li>Attend our new members orientation</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to our pastoral team.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The COP Abu Dhabi Team</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Church of Pentecost Abu Dhabi<br>
      {{churchAddress}}<br>
      Tel: {{churchPhone}}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 